Hunter’s Spending in 2015

Hunter Ratliff

January 4, 2016

Source Code: Published to: NA Author: Hunter Ratliff ([@HunterRatliff1](https://twitter.com/HunterRatliff1))

This is a quick demonstration of how R can be utilized for (non-professional) visualization of personal finances. This is totally off the cuff, and I don’t have any plans to “complete” this project at any time!

Here’s a quick figure illustrating my spending by category, by month:

In this figure, you can see how much money I have available in my checking account, plotted over the day of the month.
